{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"The greatest irony in global health"},{"time":3000,"text":"is that the poorest countries"},{"time":5000,"text":"carry the largest disease burden."},{"time":8000,"text":"If we resize the countries of the globe"},{"time":10000,"text":"in proportion to the subject of interest,"},{"time":12000,"text":"we see that Sub-Saharan Africa"},{"time":14000,"text":"is the worst hit region by HIV/AIDS."},{"time":17000,"text":"This is the most devastating epidemic of our time."},{"time":20000,"text":"We also see that this region"},{"time":22000,"text":"has the least capability in terms of dealing with the disease."},{"time":25000,"text":"There are very few doctors"},{"time":27000,"text":"and, quite frankly, these countries do not have the resources"},{"time":29000,"text":"that are needed to cope"},{"time":31000,"text":"with such epidemics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"So what the Western countries,"},{"time":35000,"text":"developed countries, have generously done"},{"time":37000,"text":"is they have proposed to provide free drugs"},{"time":39000,"text":"to all people in Third World countries"},{"time":41000,"text":"who actually can't afford these medications."},{"time":43000,"text":"And this has already saved millions of lives,"},{"time":46000,"text":"and it has prevented entire economies"},{"time":48000,"text":"from capsizing in Sub-Saharan Africa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51000,"text":"But there is a fundamental problem"},{"time":55000,"text":"that is killing the efforts"},{"time":57000,"text":"in fighting this disease,"},{"time":59000,"text":"because if you keep throwing"},{"time":61000,"text":"drugs out at people"},{"time":64000,"text":"who don't have diagnostic services,"},{"time":66000,"text":"you end up creating a problem of drug resistance."},{"time":69000,"text":"This is already beginning to happen in Sub-Saharan Africa."},{"time":72000,"text":"The problem is that,"},{"time":74000,"text":"what begins as a tragedy in the Third World"},{"time":77000,"text":"could easily become a global problem."},{"time":79000,"text":"And the last thing we want to see"},{"time":81000,"text":"is drug-resistant strains of HIV"},{"time":83000,"text":"popping up all over the world,"},{"time":85000,"text":"because it will make treatment more expensive"},{"time":88000,"text":"and it could also restore"},{"time":91000,"text":"the pre-ARV carnage of HIV/AIDS."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"I experienced this firsthand"},{"time":95000,"text":"as a high school student in Uganda."},{"time":97000,"text":"This was in the 90s"},{"time":99000,"text":"during the peak of the HIV epidemic,"},{"time":101000,"text":"before there were any ARVs in Sub-Saharan Africa."},{"time":104000,"text":"And during that time, I actually lost more relatives,"},{"time":107000,"text":"as well as the teachers who taught me,"},{"time":109000,"text":"to HIV/AIDS."},{"time":111000,"text":"So this became one of the driving passions of my life,"},{"time":114000,"text":"to help find real solutions"},{"time":117000,"text":"that could address these kinds of problems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121000,"text":"We all know about the miracle of miniaturization."},{"time":124000,"text":"Back in the day, computers used to fill this entire room,"},{"time":127000,"text":"and people actually used to work inside the computers."},{"time":130000,"text":"But what electronic miniaturization has done"},{"time":133000,"text":"is that it has allowed people to shrink"},{"time":135000,"text":"technology into a cell phone."},{"time":137000,"text":"And I'm sure everyone here enjoys cell phones"},{"time":139000,"text":"that can actually be used in the remote areas of the world,"},{"time":142000,"text":"in the Third World countries."},{"time":145000,"text":"The good news is that the same technology"},{"time":147000,"text":"that allowed miniaturization of electronics"},{"time":149000,"text":"is now allowing us to miniaturize"},{"time":152000,"text":"biological laboratories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154000,"text":"So, right now, we can actually miniaturize"},{"time":156000,"text":"biological and chemistry laboratories"},{"time":159000,"text":"onto microfluidic chips."},{"time":161000,"text":"I was very lucky to come"},{"time":163000,"text":"to the US right after high school,"},{"time":165000,"text":"and was able to work on this technology"},{"time":167000,"text":"and develop some devices."},{"time":170000,"text":"This is a microfluidic chip that I developed."},{"time":173000,"text":"A close look at how the technology works:"},{"time":175000,"text":"These are channels that are about the size of a human hair --"},{"time":178000,"text":"so you have integrated valves, pumps, mixers and injectors --"},{"time":181000,"text":"so you can fit entire diagnostic experiments"},{"time":184000,"text":"onto a microfluidic system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187000,"text":"So what I plan to do with this technology"},{"time":189000,"text":"is to actually take the current state"},{"time":191000,"text":"of the technology"},{"time":193000,"text":"and build an HIV kit"},{"time":195000,"text":"in a microfluidic system."},{"time":197000,"text":"So, with one microfluidic chip,"},{"time":199000,"text":"which is the size of an iPhone,"},{"time":202000,"text":"you can actually diagnose"},{"time":204000,"text":"100 patients at the same time."},{"time":207000,"text":"For each patient, we will be able to do"},{"time":209000,"text":"up to 100 different viral loads per patient."},{"time":212000,"text":"And this is only done in four hours,"},{"time":214000,"text":"50 times faster than the current state of the art,"},{"time":217000,"text":"at a cost that will be five to 500 times cheaper"},{"time":220000,"text":"than the current options."},{"time":222000,"text":"So this will allow us to create"},{"time":224000,"text":"personalized medicines in the Third World"},{"time":227000,"text":"at a cost that is actually achievable"},{"time":230000,"text":"and make the world a safer place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232000,"text":"I invite your interest"},{"time":234000,"text":"as well as your involvement"},{"time":236000,"text":"in driving this vision"},{"time":238000,"text":"to a point of practical reality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}